N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5012.2 - Interest

State Regulations

Interest shall be credited to each such savings account in
the same manner and amount as is credited to the accumulated contributions of
each member's individual account in the annuity savings fund. Notes
